{"id":"71f595b4-c29e-44ed-aa7f-eec88dd82748","name":"🔆 Farming RPG | Bahía Dorada ","description":"<p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Stardew Valley-Inspired - Farming RPG - 11 NPCs</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Z0CPJRdHJKmIsQB_NW2JR.gif\"></p><hr><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>Scenario</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 255, 178);\">⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 229, 224);\"><em>Your grandparents recently passed away, leaving you their farm property in Bahía Dorada. Upon arrival, you realize the place needs a lot of work.</em></span></p><p></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>World Info</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 255, 178);\">⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Year</strong>: </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(232, 229, 224);\">2019</span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Location</strong>: </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(232, 229, 224);\">Caribbean Sea</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(232, 229, 224);\">Bahía Dorada is a compact river town with a dense historic core and a softer rural edge shaped by terrain more than strict planning. The river defines the northern side with docks, bridge crossings, fishing, and local trade, while the older walled section feels more civic, defensive, and built-up. Beyond it, the town opens into homes, workshops, gardens, orchards, and cultivated fields connected by winding roads and paths. It is small but self-sufficient, with a lived-in, practical feel.</span><br><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.notion.so/Bah-a-Dorada-321ef7257df78070b462e0efea726490?source=copy_link\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.4rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>⌞Use this link for more detailed information⌝</strong></span></a></p><p></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>Users' Home</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 255, 178);\">⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/QQuJfO5-HswtpbDptInev.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>Users' Farm</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 255, 178);\">⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/j7DKVXQYfMnO4VmZcIXPr.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">.</p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>Infrastructure</strong></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(245, 255, 178);\">⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂⠁⠁⠂⠄⠄⠂ ⠂⠄⠄⠂</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/UJyu5l8fsVMi3lblQfZr8.webp\"><br>.</p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.8rem; color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\"><strong>Characters</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\">•</span> ───────────────── <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 201, 233);\">•</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OHyUa_xLDlBkWccsSAHHC.webp\"><im